      <span class="beta">beta</span>
    </div>
    <p class="tagline">Open source tooling for design systems</p>
    <p>
      Terrazzo (formerly “Cobalt UI”) is a suite of MIT-licensed open-source
      tools for generating code from tokens.
    </p>
    <div class="actions">
      <ButtonLink href="/docs">Try the Beta</ButtonLink>
      <ButtonLink
        href="https://github.com/terrazzoapp/terrazzo"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        variant="secondary">View on GitHub</ButtonLink
      >
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    Built by <a class="gh-user" href="https://github.com/drwpow"
      ><img
        class="gh-avatar"
        src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1369770?v=4"
        aria-hidden
      />@drwpow</a
    >, <a class="gh-user" href="https://github.com/ntassone"
      ><img
        class="gh-avatar"
        src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1572205?v=4"
        aria-hidden
      />@ntassone</a
    >, and <a href="https://github.com/terrazzoapp/terrazzo">others</a>.
  </footer>
